overview: Get My Links is more than a social networking community, it’s the best way for members to manage their social networking and business profiles under 1 account. Membership is Free and also ad free. It’s an easier way for people to share their Twitter, Facebook and Myspace accounts without having to send multiple links to friends and business associates.
